data.description: Don’t miss this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom single family home situated on a serene 6.35 wooded acres! This home provides the perfect getaway oasis without compromising the convenience of living near city amenities. Walk into an impressive living area with vaulted ceilings and abundant natural light pouring in through the glass sliding doors and extra large windows. The spacious kitchen/dining area includes island, wood stove, and every appliance you need to make meal preparation a breeze! The large sliding glass doors beckon you to the back deck which overlooks a stunning, private view of mature woodlands - the ideal space to unwind. This home enjoys so many stunning views! The family room sits adjacent to the kitchen and dining area and features a large bay window and spiral staircase leading to the lower level. The primary suite is conveniently tucked away on this level and features vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet, private access to the massive back deck, and its own private en-suite bathroom. The partial walk-out basement is ideal for creating additional living space or can remain as an extra storage option. Two other spacious bedrooms and bathroom complete the home. Conveniently located only 15-20 minutes from WMC, shopping, restaurants and I-37! Updates include a new furnace. If you have been waiting for a home that is nestled in woods while also easily accessible to shopping and dining - this is it! Don’t miss the opportunity to make it your own!
